exceptions.exn: In environment m : fmap d : dart t : tag p : point k : dim H : inv_hmap (I m d t p) IHm : inv_hmap m -> top m k nil = nil H1 : top m k nil = nil H2 : prec_I m d Unable to unify "nil" with "if eq_dart_dec d nil then nil else nil".

original: intros m k H. induction m. - simpl. reflexivity. - simpl. inversion H as [H1 H2]. apply IHm in H1. rewrite H1. reflexivity. - simpl. inversion H as [H1 H2]. apply IHm in H1. destruct H2 as [H2 _]. rewrite H1. reflexivity.
